<p style="margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Hi <strong><%= @order.buyer_name %></strong>,</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #374151;">
  We have received your payment details for order <strong><%= @order.order_no %></strong>.
</p>
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 20px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f9fafb;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 14px 16px;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.6px;">Status</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; color: #f59e0b;">Pending Verification</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p style="margin: 0 0 18px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #374151;">
  Our team is currently verifying your transaction. You will receive your tickets via email immediately upon approval.
</p>
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; background-color: #eff6ff;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e40af;">
      Keep an eye on your inbox for your confirmation email with tickets!
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
